\left[\begin{array}{cccc|c}       1 & 1 & 1 & 0 & 75         \\[0.55ex]       0 & 0 & -1 & 1 & 5        \\[0.55ex]       0 & -1 & 0 & 1 & 0\\[0.55ex]       0 & 0 & 0 & 3 & 75 \end{array}\right]
3D = 75 \implies D=25
D-B = 0 \implies D=B \implies B=25
D-C = 5 \implies C=25-5 \implies C=20
A+B+C = 75 \implies A=30
